<bibRefCitation author="Bistrom, O. &amp; Nilsson, A. N. &amp; Bergsten, J." box="[779,995,1914,1941]" pageId="1" pageNumber="483" pagination="1 - 379" refId="ref13976" refString="Bistrom, O., Nilsson, A. N. &amp; Bergsten, J. (2015) Taxonomic revision of Afrotropical Laccophilus Leach, 1815 (Coleoptera, Dytiscidae). ZooKeys, 542, 1 - 379. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / zookeys. 542.5975" type="journal article" year="2015">
Biström 
<emphasis box="[876,932,1915,1941]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="483">et al.</emphasis>
2015
</bibRefCitation>
